comments: Niang (SAC) places and retracts his hand from Barnes' (SAC) body at the start of the drive, and the contact is marginal.
Embiid (PHI) establishes himself in a screening position in Haliburton's (SAC) path and makes marginal contact as they disengage.
Barnes (SAC) makes marginal contact with Harris' (PHI) arm after the release of his driving shot attempt.
Curry (PHI) reaches across Haliburton's (SAC) body and makes contact with his arm after his gather, affecting his driving shot attempt.
Embiid (PHI) establishes himself in a screening position in Haliburton's (SAC) path and makes marginal contact as he releases away from the contact.
Mitchell (SAC) legally contests Maxey's (PHI) jump shot attempt.
Metu (SAC) makes marginal contact with Harris (PHI) underneath the basket and disengage as they pursue the loose ball.
Curry (PHI) does not maintain a legal guarding position in Halliburton's (SAC) path when he delivers contact, which affects Haliburton's SQBR.
Holmes (SAC) establishes himself in a screening position in Thybulle's (PHI) path, and marginal contact occurs.
Hield (SAC) brushes Thybulle's (PHI) body as he moves along the perimeter, and the contact is marginal.
Niang (PHI) slides his hand off Haliburton's (SAC) body as he dribbles on the perimeter, which doesn't affect his SQBR.
Embiid (PHI) is already in Harkless' (SAC) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Embiid (PHI) establishes himself in a screening position in Barnes' (SAC) path and makes marginal contact to his side as they disengage.
Niang (PHI) does not signal a timeout within 5 seconds. A 5-second violation is correctly whistled against PHI.
Thybulle (PHI) and Barnes (SAC) engage and disengage with one another off-ball.
Thybulle (SAC) brushes Haliburton's (SAC) left arm during his drive, which doesn't affect his SQBR or ability to pass.
Green (PHI) legally contests Barnes' (SAC) jump shot attempt.
